{
  "stem": "964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no shul that, you know-- this was the point where all the Jews congregated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I found out that in Prague-- I was de-mobilized in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I found out that in Prague, there's a place, a Jewish restaurant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were plenty of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody had his-- had his own story, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was this the first time you actually knew what had happened to the people in the camps?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were plenty of people laying around dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you're dead, you don't look if the guy is circumcised or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or in the case with women, they're all naked laying around dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you couldn't, you know, make any different-- you couldn't draw any conclusions that these people were Jewish or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the people that escaped, got through the war in the forest or the people that remained alive after concentration camp, they told me the stories what-- what really happened, how the Poles helped them, how the Poles sold them out to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is how I found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a-- when I came to that restaurant, they had a committee in those days already, a committee of the survivors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went up to the committee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I want to send a telegram.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took me a telegram to my sister, to Israel, that I am alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew that my brother in [INAUDIBLE] was working the [INAUDIBLE], he's alive, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he-- at the last minute, I had correspondence with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said that they gave him a paper that he cannot be taken to the army, because he's too valuable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an armature winder.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
